11NodeState::NodeState(std::unique_ptr<NodeDataModel> const &model)
12 : _inConnections(model->nPorts(PortType::In)), _outConnections(model->nPorts(PortType::Out)), _reaction(NOT_REACTING),
13 _reactingPortType(PortType::None), _resizing(false)
14{
15}
16std::vector<NodeState::ConnectionPtrSet> const &NodeState::getEntries(PortType portType) const
17{
18 if (portType == PortType::In)
19 return _inConnections;
20 else
21 return _outConnections;
22}
23std::vector<NodeState::ConnectionPtrSet> &NodeState::getEntries(PortType portType)
24{
25 if (portType == PortType::In)
26 return _inConnections;
27 else
28 return _outConnections;
29}
30NodeState::ConnectionPtrSet NodeState::connections(PortType portType, PortIndex portIndex) const
31{
32 auto const &connections = getEntries(portType);
33 return connections[portIndex];
34}
35void NodeState::setConnection(PortType portType, PortIndex portIndex, Connection &connection)
36{
37 auto &connections = getEntries(portType);
38 connections.at(portIndex).insert(std::make_pair(connection.id(), &connection));
39}
40void NodeState::eraseConnection(PortType portType, PortIndex portIndex, QUuid id)
41{
42 getEntries(portType)[portIndex].erase(id);
43}

56void NodeState::setReaction(ReactToConnectionState reaction, PortType reactingPortType, std::shared_ptr<NodeDataType> reactingDataType)
57{
58 _reaction = reaction;
59 _reactingPortType = reactingPortType;
60 _reactingDataType = std::move(reactingDataType);
61}
62bool NodeState::isReacting() const
63{
64 return _reaction == REACTING;
65}
